25
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:44,610
Because separating the handler and endpoint clusters makes our code more readable and easier to maintain.

26
00:01:44,610 --> 00:01:49,440
And also these structure align well with the principle of the clean architecture.

27
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:55,740
We can mapping the handle class to the application layer and mapping the endpoint class to the presentation

28
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:57,390
